the most significant “harm” caused was the

00:01:46.655 --> 00:01:49.625
potential loss of some corporate revenue

00:01:49.935 --> 00:01:52.725
and damage to the concept of copyright.

00:01:53.725 --> 00:01:56.845
And Aaron Swartz, were he still alive

00:01:56.845 --> 00:02:00.425
today, would justifiably question why he

00:02:00.425 --> 00:02:02.945
was mentioned even in the same sentence

